                                                                                                                           17                                                                                      Seagal kept woman as sex toy
          BEN LEACH                          Under siege                                  
	London, April 14: Steven Seagal, the action movie star, used one woman as a sex toy and kept others who were on call 24 hours a day to satisfy his desires, according to a former employee.        
	 Kayden Nguyen, 23, a former model, has filed a 650,000 lawsuit against the star of Under Siege and Exit Wounds.        
	Nguyen claims she was treated as a sex toy and was sexually assaulted three times after applying to be his personal assistant. The 58-year-old is also said to have kept two Russian attendants who were on call 24 hours a day to satisfy his demands. Nguyen says she was hired by Seagal as an executive assistant.                    THE DAILY TELEGRAPH                                                                                                                                                   
